%% Use case diagram: Reject Invalid Input
flowchart LR
  user((User))
  ui[Web UI]
  api["POST or PATCH /todos"]
  val[zod Validation]

  user -->|submits empty or over-long title| ui
  ui -->|sends request with invalid body| api
  api --> val
  val -->|empty title| api
  val -->|title exceeds 255 chars| api
  val -->|malformed JSON body| api
  api -->|400 with structured error details| ui
  ui -->|displays validation error message| user
